Package edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model

Contains the common model interfaces and general model constants

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Annotation
    The annotation interface contains all methods special to annotations.
    AnnotationList
    AnnotationList is a simple list of annotations without the additional metadata of pages.
    Container
    The container interface defines all methods special to containers.
    FormattableObject
    Everything that need to have a String serialization for usage in HTTP response bodies has to implement this interface.
    ModelFactory
    Interface used for creation of internal data models.
    Page
    Page objects need to implement this interface.
    WapObject
    The WapObject that is the base interface Annotation and Container extend
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContainerPreference
    Helper methods and constants for Container preferences
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FormattableObject.Type
    The different types of formattable objects that may exist
